snippet.title: Zwei II - Prologue (English-translated, enable closed captioning to read!)
snippet.description:
Prologue to Falcom's Japanese PC action RPG "Zwei II', fully translated to English by myself. Enable the English subtitles by turning on the closed captioning from the menu on the bottom-right corner of the video (it's the "CC" button).

For more information on Zwei II and its predecessor:

http://seldane.proboards.com/index.cgi?board=falcom&action=display&thread=4287
